    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Almond-shaped lights, auras, or series of lines surrounding the whole of a sacred figure, particularly in Buddhist and Christian imagery.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
